{# AI Write Walkthrough #}
<h2 class="govuk-heading-l">Using AI Write</h2>

<p class="govuk-body">
  The AI Write feature generates new content based on your prompt.
</p>

<h3 class="govuk-heading-m">Step-by-step walkthrough</h3>

<ol class="govuk-list govuk-list--number govuk-list--spaced">
  <li>
    <strong>Click the AI button</strong>
    <p class="govuk-body">
      In the CKEditor toolbar, click the AI dropdown menu
    </p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <strong>Select "AI Write"</strong>
    <p class="govuk-body">
      Choose the AI Write option from the dropdown
    </p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <strong>Enter your prompt</strong>
    <p class="govuk-body">
      Describe what content you want to create. Be specific about the topic,
      audience, and any key points to include.
    </p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <strong>Click Generate</strong>
    <p class="govuk-body">
      Wait a few seconds while the AI generates your content
    </p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <strong>Review the result</strong>
    <p class="govuk-body">
      Read through the generated content carefully
    </p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <strong>Insert or regenerate</strong>
    <p class="govuk-body">
      Click "Insert" to add the content to your page, or "Regenerate" to try again
    </p>
  </li>
</ol>

