<h3 class="govuk-heading-m">Expected results</h3>

<p class="govuk-body">
  The AI will generate structured content that typically includes:
</p>

<ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
  <li>Clear headings and subheadings</li>
  <li>Bullet points for lists of information</li>
  <li>Plain English suitable for government content</li>
  <li>Logical flow from introduction to conclusion</li>
</ul>

{# Simplify Walkthrough #}
<h2 class="govuk-heading-l">Using Simplify to Plain English</h2>

<p class="govuk-body">
  The Simplify feature rewrites selected text to be more accessible.
</p>

<h3 class="govuk-heading-m">Step-by-step walkthrough</h3>

<ol class="govuk-list govuk-list--number govuk-list--spaced">
  <li>
    <strong>Select the text</strong>
    <p class="govuk-body">
      Highlight the text you want to simplify in the editor
    </p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <strong>Click the AI button</strong>
    <p class="govuk-body">
      With text selected, click the AI dropdown menu
    </p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <strong>Select "Simplify to Plain English"</strong>
    <p class="govuk-body">
      Choose the Simplify option from the dropdown
    </p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <strong>Review the comparison</strong>
    <p class="govuk-body">
      See your original text alongside the simplified version
    </p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <strong>Toggle diff highlighting</strong>
    <p class="govuk-body">
      Use the checkbox to see exactly what changed (additions in green, removals in red)
    </p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <strong>Apply or cancel</strong>
    <p class="govuk-body">
      Click "Apply" to replace your text, or "Cancel" to keep the original
    </p>
  </li>
</ol>

