{# Try This Prompts Section #}
<h2 class="govuk-heading-l">Try this: example prompts</h2>

<p class="govuk-body">
  Here are some prompts you can try with the AI Write feature. Copy and paste
  them into the prompt field to see how the AI responds.
</p>

{# Service Page Prompt #}
<div class="ndx-prompt-card">
  <div class="ndx-prompt-card__header">
    <h3 class="govuk-heading-s govuk-!-margin-bottom-0">Service Page: Parking Permits</h3>
    <span class="govuk-tag govuk-tag--blue">Beginner</span>
  </div>
  <div class="ndx-prompt-card__body">
    <p class="govuk-body govuk-!-font-weight-bold">Prompt:</p>
    <p class="ndx-prompt-text">
      Write a service page for residents explaining how to apply for a parking permit.
      Include eligibility criteria, required documents, and processing time.
    </p>
  </div>
  <details class="govuk-details govuk-!-margin-bottom-0">
    <summary class="govuk-details__summary">
      <span class="govuk-details__summary-text">What to expect</span>
    </summary>
    <div class="govuk-details__text">
      A structured page with sections for eligibility, documents needed, how to apply,
      and processing times. The content will be in plain English suitable for council websites.
    </div>
  </details>
</div>

{# How-to Guide Prompt #}
<div class="ndx-prompt-card">
  <div class="ndx-prompt-card__header">
    <h3 class="govuk-heading-s govuk-!-margin-bottom-0">How-to Guide: Report a Pothole</h3>
    <span class="govuk-tag govuk-tag--blue">Beginner</span>
  </div>
  <div class="ndx-prompt-card__body">
    <p class="govuk-body govuk-!-font-weight-bold">Prompt:</p>
    <p class="ndx-prompt-text">
      Write a step-by-step guide for reporting potholes. Include what information
      residents need to provide, expected response time, and how to track their report.
    </p>
  </div>
  <details class="govuk-details govuk-!-margin-bottom-0">
    <summary class="govuk-details__summary">
      <span class="govuk-details__summary-text">What to expect</span>
    </summary>
    <div class="govuk-details__text">
      A numbered guide with clear steps, information about what details to include
      (location, size, photos), and what happens after reporting.
    </div>
  </details>
</div>

{# News Article Prompt #}
<div class="ndx-prompt-card">
  <div class="ndx-prompt-card__header">
    <h3 class="govuk-heading-s govuk-!-margin-bottom-0">News Article: New Recycling Service</h3>
    <span class="govuk-tag govuk-tag--green">Intermediate</span>
  </div>
  <div class="ndx-prompt-card__body">
    <p class="govuk-body govuk-!-font-weight-bold">Prompt:</p>
    <p class="ndx-prompt-text">
      Write a news article announcing a new food waste collection service starting
      next month. Include collection days, what can be recycled, and how to request a bin.
    </p>
  </div>
  <details class="govuk-details govuk-!-margin-bottom-0">
    <summary class="govuk-details__summary">
      <span class="govuk-details__summary-text">What to expect</span>
    </summary>
    <div class="govuk-details__text">
      A news-style article with a headline, lead paragraph summarising the key points,
      and body content with details about the service, dates, and how to participate.
    </div>
  </details>
</div>

{# Directory Entry Prompt #}
<div class="ndx-prompt-card">
  <div class="ndx-prompt-card__header">
    <h3 class="govuk-heading-s govuk-!-margin-bottom-0">Directory Entry: Community Centre</h3>
    <span class="govuk-tag govuk-tag--blue">Beginner</span>
  </div>
  <div class="ndx-prompt-card__body">
    <p class="govuk-body govuk-!-font-weight-bold">Prompt:</p>
    <p class="ndx-prompt-text">
      Write a directory entry for Riverside Community Centre. Include opening hours,
      facilities available, booking information, and accessibility features.
    </p>
  </div>
  <details class="govuk-details govuk-!-margin-bottom-0">
    <summary class="govuk-details__summary">
      <span class="govuk-details__summary-text">What to expect</span>
    </summary>
    <div class="govuk-details__text">
      A concise directory listing with contact details, opening times, a description
      of facilities, and information about accessibility and how to book.
    </div>
  </details>
</div>

{# Consultation Response Prompt #}
<div class="ndx-prompt-card">
  <div class="ndx-prompt-card__header">
    <h3 class="govuk-heading-s govuk-!-margin-bottom-0">Consultation: Public Feedback Summary</h3>
    <span class="govuk-tag govuk-tag--green">Intermediate</span>
  </div>
  <div class="ndx-prompt-card__body">
    <p class="govuk-body govuk-!-font-weight-bold">Prompt:</p>
    <p class="ndx-prompt-text">
      Write an introduction for a consultation page about proposed changes to local
      bus routes. Explain why the council is consulting, how residents can have
      their say, and the deadline for responses.
    </p>
  </div>
  <details class="govuk-details govuk-!-margin-bottom-0">
    <summary class="govuk-details__summary">
      <span class="govuk-details__summary-text">What to expect</span>
    </summary>
    <div class="govuk-details__text">
      An engaging introduction that explains the context, invites participation,
      and clearly states how to respond and by when.
    </div>
  </details>
</div>

{# Tips Section #}
<h2 class="govuk-heading-l">Tips for better results</h2>

<h3 class="govuk-heading-m">Be specific in your prompts</h3>

<p class="govuk-body">
  The more detail you provide, the better the result. Compare these prompts:
</p>

<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-one-half">
    <div class="ndx-example-card ndx-example-card--bad">
      <p class="govuk-body govuk-!-font-weight-bold">Less effective:</p>
      <p class="govuk-body">"Write about bins"</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-one-half">
    <div class="ndx-example-card ndx-example-card--good">
      <p class="govuk-body govuk-!-font-weight-bold">More effective:</p>
      <p class="govuk-body">"Write a guide explaining what can go in the blue recycling bin, including common mistakes residents make"</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<h3 class="govuk-heading-m">Include context and audience</h3>

<p class="govuk-body">
  Tell the AI who the content is for:
</p>

<ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
  <li>"Write for residents who have never used this service before"</li>
  <li>"Write for business owners applying for a licence"</li>
  <li>"Write in a friendly, helpful tone suitable for elderly residents"</li>
</ul>

<h3 class="govuk-heading-m">Review and edit AI output</h3>

<div class="govuk-warning-text">
  <span class="govuk-warning-text__icon" aria-hidden="true">!</span>
  <strong class="govuk-warning-text__text">
    <span class="govuk-visually-hidden">Important</span>
    Always review AI-generated content before publishing. Check for:
  </strong>
</div>

<ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
  <li><strong>Accuracy</strong> - Are the facts correct? Are dates and prices right?</li>
  <li><strong>Tone</strong> - Does it match your council's voice?</li>
  <li><strong>Completeness</strong> - Is anything missing?</li>
  <li><strong>Links</strong> - The AI cannot create links, so you'll need to add these</li>
</ul>

<h3 class="govuk-heading-m">Accessibility considerations</h3>

<p class="govuk-body">
  The AI aims to write in plain English, but always check that:
</p>

<ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
  <li>Sentences are short (under 25 words is ideal)</li>
  <li>Technical terms are explained</li>
  <li>Instructions are clear and actionable</li>
  <li>Content can be understood by someone with a reading age of 9</li>
</ul>

{# Common Mistakes #}
<h3 class="govuk-heading-m">Common mistakes to avoid</h3>

<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-one-half">
    <div class="ndx-mistake-card">
      <h4 class="govuk-heading-s">Publishing without review</h4>
      <p class="govuk-body-s">
        The AI can make mistakes or include outdated information.
        Always check facts before publishing.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-one-half">
    <div class="ndx-mistake-card">
      <h4 class="govuk-heading-s">Vague prompts</h4>
      <p class="govuk-body-s">
        One-word prompts produce generic content.
        Be specific about what you need.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="govuk-grid-row govuk-!-margin-top-4">
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-one-half">
    <div class="ndx-mistake-card">
      <h4 class="govuk-heading-s">Including sensitive data</h4>
      <p class="govuk-body-s">
        Never include personal data, case numbers, or sensitive information in prompts.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-one-half">
    <div class="ndx-mistake-card">
      <h4 class="govuk-heading-s">Expecting perfect output</h4>
      <p class="govuk-body-s">
        The AI provides a starting point, not finished content.
        Plan time for editing and refinement.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

